              To get this thread going, how about Favorite ship in eve?<BR><BR>For me (Because I can fly it, and fly it well.) is the Arazu.  The Gallente Force Recon Cruiser. I like it because of it's stealth attributes mainly. Nothing like jumping into a bubble camp, pointing a direction out of the bubble. Clicking the MWD then cloak. Moving out of the bubble and warping to some distant safe spot. The best part is sitting in that safe, or another or even warping back towards the gate all cloaked, and then taunting local. <img src="http://episteme.arstechnica.com/groupee_common/emoticons/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" width="15" height="15"><!--graemlin::)-->

              

              
              
