              My favorite ship is the one that I spent so long training for on my main.  The Nighthawk.  Its sleek black lines, symmetrical shape (for a Caldari ship that is), and the ability to just spew missiles like crazy.  Took me months of dedication to skill training to get it, but Command Ships V makes the pay off worth it.  <BR><BR>With my alts, I'd love to get my industry guy a Nomad, but since I lack the funds to get one, going to go with the Fenrir.  Nothing says serious business like a Jawa Sandcrawler.<BR><BR>Then there's the Thanatos.  'nuff said.

              

              
              
